import { Navbar, Nav, Container } from 'react-bootstrap';

const Navigation = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Navbar collapseOnSelect fixed='top' expand='sm' bg='dark' variant='white'>
                <Container>
                    <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls='responsive-navbar-nav' />
                   
                    <Navbar.Collapse id='responsive-navbar-nav'>
                        
                        <Nav>
                            
                            <Nav.Link href='/'>Home </Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href='/'>Panda</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href='/'> Gorilla</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href='/'> Rhino</Nav.Link>
                             <Nav.Link href='/'>Sea Turtle</Nav.Link>

                        </Nav>
                        

                    </Navbar.Collapse>

                </Container>

            </Navbar>
            
        </>   
    )
}
export default Navigation;
